{
  "title": "Intensely Pungent Kenyan Beef Stew",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful stew featuring tender beef and a blend of aromatic spices, cooked to perfection in a traditional ttukbaegi earthenware pot. This dish is perfect for a lazy Sunday afternoon.",
